title: The Flaming Lips’ Wayne Coyne Talks Drugs in Music, Extension Cords and Ascots
itunes:title: The Flaming Lips’ Wayne Coyne Talks Drugs in Music, Extension Cords and Ascots
description:
Wayne Coyne, the frontman for The Flaming Lips, and Fred go back to their roots-Oklahoma-and determine there's a slight chance they could be related.

Of course,  The Flaming Lips are a multi Grammy Award-winning American rock band  and were on Q magazine's list of the "50 Bands to See Before You Die" in 2002. Around since 1983, The Flaming Lips are an unquestioned pioneer for the alternative genre.

And Wayne is their leader. 

Recorded at Bourbon & Beyond
